      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MR. LASSO (2) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 5.5 lengths at Q Lakeside in a handy 25.39 beating Daytona Sunset. Has won two of three starts from this draw. Can make it two on the bounce. NEAME (8) three runs back posted a slick 29.73 win over 520m at Q Parklands then has found the minor money in two runs since. Has the ability and can find winning form again. CANYA DETONATOR (3) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (30.16) last time out at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Hard to beat again. TANK KEEPING (4) is new to this course but not to be underestimated.",
